    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Interactive Navigation Menu</h1>
        <p>This colorful navigation menu changes appearance when you scroll and when you hover over menu items. Try it out!</p>
        <button class="btn">Get Started</button>
    </section>

    <!-- Content Sections -->
    <div class="content">
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Scroll Effect</h2>
            <p>Scroll down to see the navigation menu change its background color and text colors. The menu becomes more opaque and changes to a light background with dark text when scrolled.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Hover Effects</h2>
            <p>Hover over the menu items to see colorful animations. Each item changes color and shows an underline effect with a gradient color.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Gradient Colors</h2>
            <p>This design uses vibrant gradient colors that transition smoothly. The logo and hover effects use gradient colors that change based on scroll state.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Smooth Animations</h2>
            <p>All transitions and animations are smooth and fluid, creating a pleasant user experience. The menu responds quickly to user interactions.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>Interactive Navigation Menu &copy; 2025 | Created with HTML, CSS & JavaScript</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Navbar scroll effect
        window.addEventListener('scroll', function() {
            const navbar = document.getElementById('navbar');
            if (window.scrollY > 50) {
                navbar.classList.add('scrolled');
            } else {
                navbar.classList.remove('scrolled');
            }
        });

        // Add animation to nav items on hover
        document.querySelectorAll('.nav-links a').forEach(item => {
            item.addEventListener('mouseenter', function() {
                this.style.transition = 'all 0.3s ease';
            });
        });
    </script>
